text: The 1923 Santa Clara Missionites football team was an American football team that represented Santa Clara University during the 1923 college football season. In their first season under head coach Eddie Kienholz, the Broncos compiled a 3–4–1 record. ==Schedule== ==References== Santa Clara Category:Santa Clara Broncos football seasons Santa Clara Missionites football
